hii ive made a lot of customs but this is a new one i just made wanna see wat yall think , if you wanna see all my other customs i got about 20 or so go to youtube and search "evil scape rsps" then click the one that says kalphite armour my server isnt up at the moment because i got bored all i like to do is make customs but please leave comments below of your opinions

this i just made from a dragon but tomorrow ima post a complete custom made by me not just a dragon cut up to make a platebody these items include: new staffs (elite air , water, earth,fire staffs) kalphite armour custom rapiers (looks B.A.) and custom frost dragon platebody and rapier
Credit also to Gary for the models used to create this! tytyty Gary
